import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { IServiceMap } from '../service-map.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-service-map-detail', templateUrl: './service-map-detail.component.html', }) export class ServiceMapDetailComponent implements OnInit { serviceMap: IServiceMap | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ serviceMap }) => { this.serviceMap = serviceMap; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
